name: Alive (itch) (Ell1Th3Gh0st)
description:
You wake up in a place you don't recognize. You're laying on a pile of cold stones. Everything around you is dark. Ahead of you is a doorway with white light pouring out of it.

It's your choice,

do you want to see what's on the other side?

< this story has 7 different endings >
